posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'The Lexington at Champions  | Parawest Management |', 'show contact info', 'Time to Enhance your Lifestyle!', '5007 FM 1960 Rd.', 'Houston, TX 77069', '$1400/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '954 sqft.', 'Bedrooms:', '2 Bed', 'Bathrooms:', '1 Bath', 'Parking:', '1 Off street', 'Lease Duration:', '1 Year (See Details Below)', 'Security Deposit:', 'Ask about our Security Deposit Alternative', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs OK (Pet restrictions apply)', 'Floor:', '1st or 2nd', 'Property Type:', 'Apartments', 'DESCRIPTION', 'We invite you to experience the Lexington at Champions difference – a relaxed, comfortable vibe that just feels like home.', 'Located in the heart of Northwest Houston, our premier apartment community is nestled among pine trees in the Champions area.', 'Our residents love being within walking distance to the neighborhood’s excellent shopping, dining, and entertainment district.', 'Commuting to Spring or Houston is a breeze with easy freeway access to Highway 249 and I-45 as well as the Sam Houston Toll Road.', 'RENTAL FEATURES', 'Living Room', 'Dining Room', 'Walk-In Closets', 'Fully Equipped Kitchen', 'Wood Look flooring', 'Dishwasher', 'Garden Tubs', 'Outside Storage', 'Washer and Dryer Included', 'Patio and Balconies', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'On-Site Clothes Care Center', 'Picnic Area with Grilling Stations', 'Detached Garages', 'Resident Clubhouse', 'Off-street parking', 'LEASE TERMS', 'Deposit depends on approval.', 'Criminal, credit and rental history check is required', 'CALL FOR ADDITIONAL INFO', 'The Lexington at Champions', '5007 FM 1960 Rd.', 'Houston, TX 77069', 'show contact info', 'WWW.THELEXINGTONATCHAMPIONS.COM']
